png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-115\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6} -->\n<h6><strong><span class=\"has-inline-color has-accent-color\">A MANY-OBJECTIVE EVOLUTIONARY ALGORITHM WITH TWO INTERACTING PROCESSES: CASCADE CLUSTERING AND REFERENCE POINT INCREMENTAL LEARNING</span></strong></h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hongwei Ge<strong><span class=\"has-inline-color has-accent-color\">*</span></strong>,&nbsp;<strong>Mingde Zhao<span class=\"has-inline-color has-accent-color\">*</span></strong>, Liang Sun, Zhen Wang, Guozhen Tan, Qiang Zhang, C. L. Philip Chen @ IEEE Transactions on Evolutionary Computation (TEVC), 2019.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"full\",\"id\":117,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-large\"><a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/8477679\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/fastCAR.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-117\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6} -->\n<h6><strong>A MANY-OBJECTIVE EVOLUTIONARY ALGORITHM WITH FAST CLUSTERING AND REFERENCE POINT REDISTRIBUTION</strong></h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Mingde Zhao</strong>, Hongwei Ge, Hongyan Han, Liang Sun @ IEEE Congress on Evolutionary Computation (CEC), 2018.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Software and Patents</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"full\",\"id\":126,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-large\"><a href=\"https://github.com/PwnerHarry/SOOPLAT\"><img src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/SOOPLAT.png\" alt=\"\